    "en": {
      "title": "Aragalaya President Wickremesinghe should have initiated dialogue with protesters - Mano Ganesan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Wickremesinghe told party leaders, he will provide Vihara Maha Devi Gardens to protesters",
        "After all the Aragalaya people sent former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa home",
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe should have initiated a dialogue with the Aragalaya protesters, Tamil Progressive Alliance (TPA) Leader Mano Ganesan said yesterday.",
        "\u201cPresident Wickremesinghe told party leaders, he will provide Vihara Maha Devi Gardens to protesters. Now, what prevented him from forwarding his proposal to protesters and initiating a peaceful transfer of location?\u201d he questioned.",
        "\u201cAfter all the Aragalaya people sent former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa home, hence, Wickremesinghe is President today\u201d he added."
      ],
